# ByteStrike - Complete System Overview

ByteStrike is a GPU compute futures trading platform. Users trade perpetual contracts where the price tracks real-world GPU hourly rental rates (H100, B200, H200, T4, etc.) from major cloud providers. The platform runs on Ethereum Sepolia testnet.

